    <summary type="html">&lt;!-- [DocumentBodyStart:f45ca0aa-c584-463e-b4ef-2954ddf88c01] --&gt;&lt;div class="jive-rendered-content"&gt;&lt;p&gt;Hello,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="min-height: 8pt; height: 8pt; padding: 0px;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;I am trying to access a file that is located in the WEB-INF folder.&amp;nbsp; In particular, I have the following line of code in the init() handler of a servlet:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="min-height: 8pt; height: 8pt; padding: 0px;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;InputStream s = servletContext.getResourceAsStream(sPath);&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="min-height: 8pt; height: 8pt; padding: 0px;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;where sPath = File.separator+"WEB-INF"+File.separator+"filename.ini";&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="min-height: 8pt; height: 8pt; padding: 0px;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;I have been running this under Tomcat 7 with no problem but I am trying to switch over to JBoss 7.1 and with no other changes the same code now returns a NULL. Can someone explain why this is failing under JBoss when it used to work under Tomcat?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="min-height: 8pt; height: 8pt; padding: 0px;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Thank you,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Al&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!-- [DocumentBodyEnd:f45ca0aa-c584-463e-b4ef-2954ddf88c01] --&gt;&lt;img src='/beacon?t=1378895115606' /&gt;</summary>
